### ===========================================
### Jobs - Change Status
### ===========================================

### 1. Start Job (Activo)
POST {{baseUrl}}/Jobs/changeStatus
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "jobId": 12345,
    "newJobStatus": 1,
    "comment": "Iniciando job",
    "latitude": 14.634915,
    "longitude": -90.506882
}

### 2. Pause Job (Pausado)
POST {{baseUrl}}/Jobs/changeStatus
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "jobId": 12345,
    "newJobStatus": 2,
    "comment": "Pausando job por almuerzo",
    "latitude": 14.634915,
    "longitude": -90.506882
}

### 3. Complete Job (Finalizado)
POST {{baseUrl}}/Jobs/changeStatus
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "jobId": 12345,
    "newJobStatus": 3,
    "statusChangeDate": "2025-12-18T17:30:00",
    "comment": "Job completado exitosamente",
    "latitude": 14.634915,
    "longitude": -90.506882,
    "totalExecutionTime": 7200
}

### 4. Mark as Incomplete (Incompleto)
POST {{baseUrl}}/Jobs/changeStatus
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "jobId": 12345,
    "newJobStatus": 4,
    "comment": "No se pudo completar por falta de materiales",
    "latitude": 14.634915,
    "longitude": -90.506882
}

### 5. Reschedule Job (Programado)
POST {{baseUrl}}/Jobs/changeStatus
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "jobId": 12345,
    "newJobStatus": 6,
    "comment": "Reprogramado para mañana",
    "latitude": 14.634915,
    "longitude": -90.506882
}

### 6. Cancel Job (Cancelado)
POST {{baseUrl}}/Jobs/changeStatus
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "jobId": 12345,
    "newJobStatus": 7,
    "comment": "Cancelado por solicitud del cliente",
    "latitude": 14.634915,
    "longitude": -90.506882
}

### ===========================================
### Job Status Reference:
### 0 - Eliminado
### 1 - Activo (Usuario lo inició)
### 2 - Pausado
### 3 - Finalizado
### 4 - Incompleto
### 5 - Reprogramado
### 6 - Programado (Pendiente de inicio)
### 7 - Cancelado
### 8 - Pendiente
### ===========================================

### ===========================================
### Parameters:
### - jobId: ID del job (requerido)
### - newJobStatus: Nuevo estado (requerido)
### - statusChangeDate: Fecha/hora del cambio (opcional, default: UTC now)
### - comment: Comentario del cambio (opcional)
### - latitude: Latitud de ubicación (opcional)
### - longitude: Longitud de ubicación (opcional)
### - totalExecutionTime: Tiempo total en segundos (opcional, para finalización)
### ===========================================

